survey_response.review_text: I traveled all the way from oman to see dr tejal podar, I was told in oman that I can not conceive. For someone who has been struggling from PCOS and PTSD I grappled  every hour of time. When I entered the clinic I saw a picture that says "nothing is impossible" and that actually happened. When I met Dr tejal she made me understand each thing very briefly, without commenting on my weight or judging me. I will vist her again for IVF after 6 months of treatment which was given by her.. I was head over heels when I got my period without taking any medicine and this happened first time in 4 years. I highly recommend Dr tejal podar she has such an endearing personality no one walks out being downhearted.

Experience we had with Little fertility clinic under Dr. Tejal is highly infinitely positive and relaxing as reluctance, doubts and fear we had got cleared the time me and my wife together first visited Dr Tejal. 

she is very approachable, professional, focused, understanding and caring. 

Both me and my wife had so many difficulties deciding which doctor to approach for our beginning and somehow decision we made to be under guidance of Dr Tejal is something we will never regret.

Thank You Dr. Tejal Poddar for being a true hope for us.

My experience with Dr. Tejal Poddar has been very good. She is a friendly, approachable and competent doctor who guided and advised me well. I was quite relaxed and at ease both during the tests carried out and at the time of the actual operation. Recommended healing is six weeks but when I was discharged after two days I was up and about and literally walking round the town like nothing had happened! Wish you all the success as you heal your patients with your smile and your little magic wand Doc!

I found out i was pregnant and was looking for gynaecologists close to home. She had amazing reviews so we went to her for first checkup. Loved how she was always just a call away, be it day or night! Had a lot of questions which she was very patient to answer throughout the 9 months. Excellent and frank advice.
